\c 14
\s Mhuka dzakanaka nedzisina kunaka
\p
\v 1 Muri vana vaJehovha Mwari wenyu. Hamungazvicheki kana kuita mhanza pakati pemeso enyu nekuda kwevakafa.
\v 2 Nokuti uri rudzi rutsvene kuna Jehovha Mwari wako; uye Jehovha wakakusarudza kuva rudzi rwakasanangurwa kwaari kubva pamarudzi ese ari panyika.
\p
\v 3 Usadya chinhu chipi nechipi chinonyangadza.
\v 4 Idzi imhuka dzamungadya: Nzombe, gwai, nembudzi;
\v 5 nondo, nemhara, nemhembwe, nembudzi yemusango, nemharapara, nemombe yemusango, nengururu.
\v 6 Nemhuka ipi neipi yakaparadzanisa mahwanda, inoparadzanisa zvakaparadzana kuva mahwanda maviri, inodzeya pakati pemhuka, iyo mungadya.
\v 7 Asi idzi hamungadzidyi pane dzinodzeya uye pane dzinoparadzanisa mahwanda: Kamera, netsuro, nembira; nokuti dzinodzeya asi hadziparadzanisi mahwanda; hadzina kuchena kwamuri.
\v 8 Nenguruve, nokuti inoparadzanisa mahwanda asi haidzeyi; haina kuchena kwamuri; musadya zvenyama yadzo, uye musagunzva zvitunha zvadzo.
\p
\v 9 Izvi muchadya pane zvese zviri mumvura: Zvese zvine zvipapiro nemakwanda mungadya.
\v 10 Asi chipi nechipi chisina zvipapiro nemakwanda musazvidya; hazvina kuchena kwamuri.
\p
\v 11 Shiri dzese dzakachena mungadya.
\v 12 Asi hamungadyi pane idzi: Gora, negondo, nenyamudzura,
\v 13 nerukodzi, nenjerere, neruvangu nemarudzi arwo,
\v 14 negunguvo ripi neripi nemarudzi aro,
\v 15 nemhou, nezizi, neshiri yegungwa, neruvangu nemarudzi aro,
\v 16 nezizi diki, nekanyurura-hove, nezizi guru,
\v 17 nekondo, nejichidza, nekanyurura-hove,
\v 18 neshuramurove, nekondo nemarudzi ayo, nemhupupu, nechiremwaremwa.
\v 19 Nezvipembenene zvese zvine mapapiro hazvina kuchena kwamuri; hazvidyiwi.
\v 20 Shiri dzese dzakachena mungadzidya.
\p
\v 21 Musadya chakafa chega; uchachipa kumweni uri mukati memasuwo ako, kuti achidye, kana ungachitengesa kumutorwa; nokuti uri rudzi rutsvene kuna Jehovha Mwari wako. Usabika mbudzana mumukaka wamai vayo.
\s Zvegumi
\p
\v 22 Uchapa zvirokwazvo chegumi chechibereko chese chembeu dzako, munda waunobereka gore negore.
\v 23 Zvino uchadya pamberi paJehovha Mwari wako, panzvimbo yaachatsaura kuisa zita rakepo, chegumi chezviyo zvako, nechewaini yako, nechemafuta ako, nechematangwe emombe dzako neemakwai ako, kuti udzidze kutya Jehovha Mwari wako mazuva ese.
\v 24 Zvino kana nzira yakarebesa kwauri zvekuti haugoni kuzvitakura, nokuti iri kuresa newe nzvimbo Jehovha Mwari wako yaakasarudza kuisa zita rakepo, kana Jehovha Mwari wako akuropafadza,
\v 25 ipapo uchazvishandura zvive mari, usungire mari muruoko rwako, ugoenda kunzvimbo Jehovha Mwari wako yaakasarudza,
\v 26 ndokutenga nemari iyo chingava chipi chinoshuviwa nemweya wako, mombe kana makwai kana waini kana zvinonwiwa zvichidhaka kana chingava chipi mweya wako chaunoshuva, zvino uchadyirapo pamberi paJehovha Mwari wako, ufare iwe neimba yako.
\v 27 Uye muRevhi ari mukati memasuwo ako, usamusiya, nokuti haana mugove kana nhaka newe.
\p
\v 28 Pakupera kwemakore matatu uchauya nechegumi chese chezvibereko zvako mugore iro, ugozviisa mukati memasuwo ako.
\v 29 Zvino muRevhi, sezvo asina mugove kana nhaka pamwe newe, nemweni, nenherera, nechirikadzi, vari mukati memasuwo ako, vachauya vadye vagute; kuti Jehovha Mwari wako akuropafadze pabasa reruoko rwako raunoita.